gomodel:ev_w_id_R-HSA-1980074_RO_0002233_R-HSA-157655_R-HSA-1980074_Reactome_R-HSA-2122948_R-HSA-1980074_enabled_by_UniProt_Q86YT6_R-HSA-1980074_controller
